# Build context hygiene: never ship host artifacts or secrets into images.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/out
**/build
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# secrets / env — provided at runtime, never baked in
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.local
**/firebase-service-account.json
CREDENTIALS.md
apps/api/test-e2e/.state.json

# vcs / tooling / docs not needed at build
.git
.github
.idea
.vscode
*.log
extracted-frontend-screens
docs
infra/scripts/*.local
